sbians assaulted and raped because of their sexual orientation\u2019121 \u2022 \u2018the risk to human rights defenders working to uphold the rights of [lesbian, gay and bisexual] persons, some of whom have been", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "31647a8f-8c5d-459e-a466-57b17f62aa60": {"__data__": {"id_": "31647a8f-8c5d-459e-a466-57b17f62aa60", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/promoting-and-protecting-human-rights-relation-sexual-orientation-gender-identity-and-sex-characteristics-manual-national", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "Promoting and Protecting Human Rights in relation to Sexual Orientation, Gender Identity and Sex Characteristics: A Manual for National Human Rights Institutions", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/promoting-and-protecting-human-rights-relation-sexual-orientation-gender-identity-and-sex-characteristics-manual-national", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "b0c9eed4e68a20490116a232fce55fbe6fc2c6684754838fee45ced6b6dd1992"}, "3": {"node_id": "3520b594-afed-4e4c-adcc-130ba203de40", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/promoting-and-protecting-human-rights-relation-sexual-orientation-gender-identity-and-sex-characteristics-manual-national", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "1c52d0527334fe72ab31f29081ca1867884b0f95677f76a210601c83e2cb1fe5"}}, "hash"